// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <case> => Statement
//  <case>* => List<Statement>
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <empty bracket pair>* => List<Object>
//  <empty bracket pair>** => List<Object>
//  <exp1> => Exp
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp5> => Exp
//  <exp6> => Exp
//  <exp7> => Exp
//  <exp8> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <expList> => ExpList
//  <inst var decl> => Decl
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <next exp> => Exp
//  <next exp>* => List<Exp>
//  <program> => Program
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 7: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ `}
// 8: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 9: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `}
// 10: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ `}
// 11: <type> ::= `int
// 12: <type> ::= `boolean
// 13: <type> ::= `void
// 14: <type> ::= `null
// 15: <type> ::= ID
// 16: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 17: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 18: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 19: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 20: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 21: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 22: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 23: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 24: <stmt> ::= `for `( <assign> `; <exp> `; <assign> `) <stmt>
// 25: <stmt> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 26: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 27: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 28: <assign> ::= ID `++
// 29: <assign> ::= `++ ID
// 30: <assign> ::= ID `--
// 31: <assign> ::= `-- ID
// 32: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 33: <stmt> ::= `;
// 34: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ <case>* `}
// 35: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ `}
// 36: <case> ::= `case <exp> `;
// 37: <exp> ::= <exp8>
// 38: <exp8> ::= <exp7>
// 39: <exp7> ::= <exp6>
// 40: <exp6> ::= <exp5>
// 41: <exp5> ::= <exp4>
// 42: <exp4> ::= <exp3>
// 43: <exp3> ::= <exp2>
// 44: <exp2> ::= <exp1>
// 45: <exp8> ::= <exp8> `|| <exp7>
// 46: <exp7> ::= <exp7> `&& <exp6>
// 47: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `== <exp5>
// 48: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `!= <exp5>
// 49: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `< <exp4>
// 50: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `<= <exp4>
// 51: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `> <exp4>
// 52: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `+ <exp3>
// 53: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `- <exp3>
// 54: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `* <exp2>
// 55: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `/ <exp2>
// 56: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `% <exp2>
// 57: <exp2> ::= `( <type> `) <exp1>
// 58: <exp2> ::= `+ <exp1>
// 59: <exp2> ::= `- <exp1>
// 60: <exp2> ::= `! <exp1>
// 61: <exp1> ::= ID
// 62: <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 63: <exp1> ::= INTLIT
// 64: <exp1> ::= STRINGLIT
// 65: <exp1> ::= CHARLIT
// 66: <exp1> ::= <exp1> `. ID
// 67: <exp1> ::= `this
// 68: <exp1> ::= `true
// 69: <exp1> ::= `false
// 70: <exp1> ::= `null
// 71: <exp1> ::= `new ID `( `)
// 72: <exp1> ::= `new <type> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `] <empty bracket pair>**
// 73: <exp1> ::= `new <type> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `] !<empty bracket pair>
// 74: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 75: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 76: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 77: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 78: any ::= {0..127}
// 79: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 80: ws ::= " "
// 81: ws ::= {10}
// 82: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 83: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 84: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 85: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 86: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x" ws*
// 87: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x"
// 88: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 89: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 90: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 91: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 92: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 93: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 94: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 95: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 96: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 97: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 98: `for ::= "#" "f" "o" ws*
// 99: `for ::= "#" "f" "o"
// 100: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 101: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 102: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 103: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 104: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 105: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 106: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 107: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 108: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 109: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 110: `new ::= "#" "n" "e" ws*
// 111: `new ::= "#" "n" "e"
// 112: `case ::= "#" "c" "e" ws*
// 113: `case ::= "#" "c" "e"
// 114: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 115: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 116: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w" ws*
// 117: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w"
// 118: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 119: `! ::= "!"
// 120: `!= ::= "@" "!" ws*
// 121: `!= ::= "@" "!"
// 122: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 123: `% ::= "%"
// 124: `&& ::= "@" "&" ws*
// 125: `&& ::= "@" "&"
// 126: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 127: `* ::= "*"
// 128: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 129: `( ::= "("
// 130: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 131: `) ::= ")"
// 132: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 133: `{ ::= "{"
// 134: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 135: `} ::= "}"
// 136: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 137: `- ::= "-"
// 138: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 139: `+ ::= "+"
// 140: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 141: `= ::= "="
// 142: `== ::= "@" "=" ws*
// 143: `== ::= "@" "="
// 144: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 145: `[ ::= "["
// 146: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 147: `] ::= "]"
// 148: `|| ::= "@" "|" ws*
// 149: `|| ::= "@" "|"
// 150: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 151: `< ::= "<"
// 152: `<= ::= "@" "<" ws*
// 153: `<= ::= "@" "<"
// 154: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 155: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 156: `. ::= "." ws*
// 157: `. ::= "."
// 158: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 159: `; ::= ";"
// 160: `++ ::= "@" "+" ws*
// 161: `++ ::= "@" "+"
// 162: `-- ::= "@" "-" ws*
// 163: `-- ::= "@" "-"
// 164: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 165: `/ ::= "/"
// 166: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 167: ID ::= letter128
// 168: ID ::= letter idChar* $$0
// 169: ID ::= letter $$0
// 170: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$1
// 171: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$1
// 172: INTLIT ::= digit128 ws*
// 173: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 174: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$2
// 175: INTLIT ::= "0" $$2
// 176: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 177: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 178: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$3
// 179: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$3
// 180: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 181: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 182: idChar ::= letter
// 183: idChar ::= digit
// 184: idChar ::= "_"
// 185: idChar128 ::= letter128
// 186: idChar128 ::= digit128
// 187: idChar128 ::= {223}
// 188: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 189: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 190: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 191: digit* ::= digit
// 192: any* ::= any* any
// 193: any* ::= any
// 194: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 195: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 196: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit
// 197: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit
// 198: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 199: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 200: <case>* ::= <case>* <case>
// 201: <case>* ::= <case>
// 202: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 203: idChar* ::= idChar
// 204: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>
// 205: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <class decl>
// 206: <empty bracket pair>** ::= <empty bracket pair>* !<empty bracket pair>
// 207: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 208: ws* ::= ws
// 209: <empty bracket pair>* ::= <empty bracket pair>* <empty bracket pair>
// 210: <empty bracket pair>* ::= <empty bracket pair>
// 211: $$0 ::= idChar128 ws*
// 212: $$0 ::= idChar128
// 213: $$1 ::= digit128 ws*
// 214: $$1 ::= digit128
// 215: $$2 ::= hexDigit128 ws*
// 216: $$2 ::= hexDigit128
// 217: $$3 ::= any128 ws*
// 218: $$3 ::= any128

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 71
        "#" => shift: 591
        ws => shift: 428
        <program> => shift: 608
        `class => shift: 426
        <start> => shift: 549
        ws* => shift: 309
        {10} => shift: 31
        " " => shift: 101
        <class decl> => shift: 538
**** STATE 1 ****
    -----------------------
**** STATE 2 ****
    `. ::= "." <%> ws* // ID
    `. ::= "." [ws*] <%> // ID
    -----------------------
    ws ::= <%> " " // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ID
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ID
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ID
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        {199..218 231..250} => reduce: 157
        "w" => reduce: 157
        "u" => reduce: 157
        "s" => reduce: 157
        "o" => reduce: 157
        "i" => reduce: 157

        " " => shift: 101
        ws* => shift: 34
        {"A".."Z" "d" "g" "j".."k" "m" "q" "y".."z"} => reduce: 157
        ws => shift: 428
        {10} => shift: 31

**** STATE 3 ****
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `!=
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%

    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // ID

    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%

    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `;
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `<
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `<=
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `=
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `==

**** STATE 8 ****

        {"1".."9"} => shift: 265
        STRINGLIT => shift: 136
        letter128 => shift: 450

    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // $

    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // <decl in class>
